Taunton.Enoch Williams House:
The Enoch Williams House is a historic house located at 616 Middleboro Avenue in Taunton, Massachusetts.


== Description and history ==
Built in 1850, the 1-1/2 story, Greek Revival style farm house is set on a side hall plan, with a front gable with a recessed wing and attached barn. The entrance features side lights with a pilaster and entablature surround.
